TITLE Create Explicit Component Variants
CREATE EXPLICIT COMPONENT VARIANTS
IO one component with many boolean props, create explicit variant components. Each variant composes the pieces it needs. The code documents itself. 
Incorrect (one component, many modes): 
CODE tsx 150CHARS
Correct (explicit variants): 
CODE tsx 171CHARS
Each implementation is unique, explicit and self-contained. Yet they can each use shared parts. 
Implementation: 
CODE tsx 1281CHARS
Each variant is explicit about: 
What provider/state it uses What UI elements it includes What actions are available 
No boolean prop combinations to reason about. No impossible states. 